The paper proposes a deep learning approach for unsupervised clustering, which falls under the category of machine learning. Specifically, the paper focuses on deep learning and nonparametric clustering, which are subfields of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
